# exclude the dev test suite from the published "fglpkg" source package
# (not needed to run the tool; keeps the artifact to just the 27 modules
# + launcher + manifest)
# NOTE: no trailing slash -- a dirOnly (trailing-slash) pattern never
# actually excludes anything here, since stageBDLFiles always calls
# shouldExclude(relPath, false) with isDir hardcoded false (see
# internal/cli/cli.go's stageBDLFiles + internal/cli/ignore.go's
# shouldExclude); a bare "test" segment-match pattern works instead.
test
